parameters: We've been caught in a trap.
This isn't the time to deliberate calmly!
Get ready for a beating, you silly bastard.
I will not forgive anyone who hurts my friends.
You're not from these parts, that's for sure.
Hey, those guys set this up first.
You're the one who should apologize.
We are the hunters, and you are the prey.
Prey should be hunted without question.
What is this girl even saying?
I see, you're "working hard" out here...
Hey, what are you laughing at?
No, we were the ones who were careless.
The hunters did what they had to do──
I came here on the recommendation of Miss Tahati.
...It appears you aren't prey after all.
I appreciate that it wasn't too complicated
Don't come to the hunting grounds while we hunt.
You'll get caught up by mistake.
Oh, so that's why the ones back in
Miss Muracca, why are you out hunting?
We hunt to get food to live day by day.
That's why I have to work harder.
Does food have any meaning in a world of immortals?
what happens to the food when they're eaten then...?
The rule of life is to eat or be eaten.
So that doesn't change, even in Parlates...
I'll need to ask Tahati about it someday.
I-I... can't give you the Mana Vessel.
Is it due to the food shortage?
We just couldn't afford to give it more.
Should I just tell Miss Tahati that you
The management of this star is not going well...
This is bad for the whole of Parlates.
It's definitely a problem that requires
some attention, at the very least.
why is there a food shortage in the first place?
Aren't they just eating too much?
There's not much of a reason.
This star... hasn't been anything but harsh.
That isn't acting strange anymore, that's
not even acting! Heck, go find them already!
Then please allow me to do it in your stead.
I can't help you with hunting,
but I can help you find missing people.
Where did your companions disappear to, exactly?
Near the eastern edge of the cliff.
Then we shall head there posthaste.
Don't worry, we won't interfere with your hunt.
Won't you become one of us?
Hey, I don't want to be a hunter!
But you guys rely on me.
To the place where they disappear, huh?
To the cliff to the east, she said.
